com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes

Class ConfigValueNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.AbstractConfigNode
      • com.wookler.zconfig.common.model.nodes.ConfigValueNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConfigValue<java.lang.String>

    public class ConfigValueNode
extends AbstractConfigNode
implements IConfigValue<java.lang.String>
    Class represents a configuration value element. All configuration values are treated as String values and converters provided to get a specific value type.

    JSON: 

         name : value,
     ...

    XML:
